                        <interp inst="t18630406-name-505" type="given" value="HERBERT"></interp>HERBERT MINTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I was with the other two witnesses, and saw the prisoner go up to Richardson, put his hand into his waistcoat-pocket, and take hold of the purse—he did not take it quite out.</p>
               <p>
